# Calc Folder

The `Calc` folder contains the calculator-related modules and supporting files for the `JSPTH` project. It is intended to house implementation code, utilities, and documentation for arithmetic operations, formula parsing, and any helper classes or functions used by the calculator functionality.

Typical contents may include:
- Python modules for calculator operations
- Unit tests for calculation logic
- Supporting documentation and examples
- Configuration or data files relevant to the calculator

This folder serves as the main location for all calculator-related development within the project.